   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "796ea013",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Реранжирование предиктов на rus-scifact через DeepSeek API\n",
    "\n",
    "Пайплайн:\n",
    "1. Загрузка предиктов (`predictions.json`) и датасета `kaengreg/rus-scifact` (queries, qrels, corpus).\n",
    "2. Подсчёт **baseline** метрик: nDCG@5, nDCG@10, Recall@5, Recall@10, MAP@5, MAP@10.\n",
    "3. **Listwise-реранжирование** топ-10 кандидатов через `deepseek-chat`.\n",
    "4. Подсчёт тех же метрик после реранжирования.\n",
    "5. Сравнительная таблица (baseline vs reranked, дельты).\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5d2ef6b1",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 0. Установка зависимостей"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "60e0e2dd",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# !pip install -q datasets openai numpy pandas tqdm"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "7d30a613",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Импорты и конфигурация"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "eb7ed427",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import json\n",
    "import os\n",
    "import re\n",
    "import time\n",
    "import math\n",
    "from pathlib import Path\n",
    "from typing import Dict, List\n",
    "from concurrent.futures import ThreadPoolExecutor, as_completed\n",
    "\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "from tqdm.auto import tqdm\n",
    "from datasets import load_dataset\n",
    "from openai import OpenAI  # DeepSeek API совместим с openai SDK\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "# ── Конфиг ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "PREDS_PATH = \"predictions.json\"          # путь к json с предиктами\n",
    "DEEPSEEK_API_KEY_PLACEHOLDER"DEEPSEEK_API_KEY\") or \"sk-...\"  # ← подставь свой ключ\n",
    "DEEPSEEK_MODEL = \"deepseek-chat\"\n",
    "KS = (5, 10)\n",
    "MAX_WORKERS = 8                          # параллельные запросы к API\n",
    "OUT_DIR = Path(\"./out\")\n",
    "OUT_DIR.mkdir(exist_ok=True)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "15e88090",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Метрики IR\n",
    "\n",
    "- **nDCG@k** — DCG нормированный на идеальный DCG, веса `1 / log2(i+2)`.\n",
    "- **Recall@k** — доля релевантных, попавших в топ-k.\n",
    "- **MAP@k** — average precision, усечённый до k, нормированный на `min(|rel|, k)`."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "bb987ba4",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def dcg(rels: List[int]) -> float:\n",
    "    return sum(r / math.log2(i + 2) for i, r in enumerate(rels))\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def ndcg_at_k(predicted: List[str], relevant: set, k: int) -> float:\n",
    "    rels = [1 if d in relevant else 0 for d in predicted[:k]]\n",
    "    ideal = sorted(rels, reverse=True)\n",
    "    idcg = dcg(ideal)\n",
    "    return dcg(rels) / idcg if idcg > 0 else 0.0\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def recall_at_k(predicted: List[str], relevant: set, k: int) -> float:\n",
    "    if not relevant:\n",
    "        return 0.0\n",
    "    hit = sum(1 for d in predicted[:k] if d in relevant)\n",
    "    return hit / len(relevant)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def map_at_k(predicted: List[str], relevant: set, k: int) -> float:\n",
    "    if not relevant:\n",
    "        return 0.0\n",
    "    score, hits = 0.0, 0\n",
    "    for i, d in enumerate(predicted[:k]):\n",
    "        if d in relevant:\n",
    "            hits += 1\n",
    "            score += hits / (i + 1)\n",
    "    return score / min(len(relevant), k)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def evaluate(preds: Dict[str, List[str]], qrels: Dict[str, set], ks=KS) -> Dict[str, float]:\n",
    "    \"\"\"Усреднённые метрики по всем queries (только тем, для которых есть qrels).\"\"\"\n",
    "    bucket = {f\"{m}@{k}\": [] for m in (\"nDCG\", \"Recall\", \"MAP\") for k in ks}\n",
    "    for qid, ranked in preds.items():\n",
    "        rel = qrels.get(qid, set())\n",
    "        if not rel:\n",
    "            continue\n",
    "        for k in ks:\n",
    "            bucket[f\"nDCG@{k}\"].append(ndcg_at_k(ranked, rel, k))\n",
    "            bucket[f\"Recall@{k}\"].append(recall_at_k(ranked, rel, k))\n",
    "            bucket[f\"MAP@{k}\"].append(map_at_k(ranked, rel, k))\n",
    "    return {m: float(np.mean(v)) if v else 0.0 for m, v in bucket.items()}\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "451933a4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Загрузка данных"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "98406745",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 3.1 Предикты\n",
    "with open(PREDS_PATH, encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n",
    "    preds_raw = json.load(f)\n",
    "\n",
    "preds: Dict[str, List[str]] = {str(k): [str(x) for x in v] for k, v in preds_raw.items()}\n",
    "lens = [len(v) for v in preds.values()]\n",
    "print(f\"queries: {len(preds)}, длина списка предиктов: min={min(lens)}, max={max(lens)}, mean={np.mean(lens):.1f}\")\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "dc6c4c97",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 3.2 Датасет kaengreg/rus-scifact\n",
    "queries_ds = load_dataset(\"kaengreg/rus-scifact\", \"queries\", split=\"queries\")\n",
    "corpus_ds  = load_dataset(\"kaengreg/rus-scifact\", \"corpus\",  split=\"corpus\")\n",
    "qrels_ds   = load_dataset(\"kaengreg/rus-scifact\", \"qrels\",   split=\"test\")\n",
    "\n",
    "queries: Dict[str, str]  = {str(r[\"_id\"]): r[\"text\"] for r in queries_ds}\n",
    "corpus:  Dict[str, dict] = {str(r[\"_id\"]): {\"title\": r.get(\"title\", \"\"), \"text\": r[\"text\"]} for r in corpus_ds}\n",
    "\n",
    "qrels: Dict[str, set] = {}\n",
    "for r in qrels_ds:\n",
    "    qid = str(r[\"query-id\"])\n",
    "    did = str(r[\"corpus-id\"])\n",
    "    if int(r.get(\"score\", 1)) > 0:\n",
    "        qrels.setdefault(qid, set()).add(did)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"queries: {len(queries)} | corpus: {len(corpus)} | qrels: {len(qrels)}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Оставляем только те queries из предиктов, для которых есть qrels\n",
    "preds = {qid: dids for qid, dids in preds.items() if qid in qrels}\n",
    "print(f\"После фильтра по qrels: {len(preds)} queries для оценки\")\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "4ca3d3df",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Baseline-метрики"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "3191cbd0",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "baseline = evaluate(preds, qrels, ks=KS)\n",
    "pd.DataFrame([baseline]).T.rename(columns={0: \"value\"}).round(4)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "653c1137",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. Listwise-реранжирование через DeepSeek\n",
    "\n",
    "Для каждого query формируется один промпт с запросом и 10 документами-кандидатами (заголовок + сниппет). Модель возвращает JSON-массив ID в новом порядке. Парсер устойчив к мусору: достаёт массив регуляркой, фильтрует только допустимые ID, дедуплицирует и добивает недостающие исходным порядком."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "b4ee7675",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "RERANK_PROMPT = \"\"\"Ты — реранкер для научного IR. Тебе дан запрос и список из {n} документов-кандидатов с их идентификаторами. Переупорядочи документы по убыванию релевантности запросу.\n",
    "\n",
    "Запрос: {query}\n",
    "\n",
    "Кандидаты:\n",
    "{candidates}\n",
    "\n",
    "Верни СТРОГО JSON-массив идентификаторов документов в новом порядке (от самого релевантного к наименее). Никакого другого текста, никаких комментариев. Пример формата: [\"id1\",\"id2\",...]\"\"\"\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def build_candidates_block(doc_ids: List[str], corpus: Dict[str, dict], max_chars: int = 600) -> str:\n",
    "    lines = []\n",
    "    for did in doc_ids:\n",
    "        d = corpus.get(did, {})\n",
    "        title = (d.get(\"title\") or \"\").strip()\n",
    "        text  = (d.get(\"text\") or \"\").strip()\n",
    "        snippet = (title + \". \" + text).strip(\". \")\n",
    "        if len(snippet) > max_chars:\n",
    "            snippet = snippet[:max_chars] + \"…\"\n",
    "        lines.append(f\"[{did}] {snippet}\")\n",
    "    return \"\\n\".join(lines)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def parse_ranked_ids(raw: str, allowed: List[str]) -> List[str]:\n",
    "    \"\"\"Парсит JSON-список ID; добивает недостающие исходным порядком.\"\"\"\n",
    "    allowed_set = set(allowed)\n",
    "    ranked: List[str] = []\n",
    "    try:\n",
    "        m = re.search(r\"\\[.*\\]\", raw, re.DOTALL)\n",
    "        if m:\n",
    "            arr = json.loads(m.group(0))\n",
    "            ranked = [str(x).strip() for x in arr if str(x).strip() in allowed_set]\n",
    "    except Exception:\n",
    "        ranked = []\n",
    "    seen = set()\n",
    "    ranked = [x for x in ranked if not (x in seen or seen.add(x))]\n",
    "    for did in allowed:\n",
    "        if did not in seen:\n",
    "            ranked.append(did)\n",
    "            seen.add(did)\n",
    "    return ranked\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "d16e0911",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def rerank_one(client: OpenAI, query: str, doc_ids: List[str], corpus: Dict[str, dict],\n",
    "               model: str = DEEPSEEK_MODEL, retries: int = 3) -> List[str]:\n",
    "    prompt = RERANK_PROMPT.format(\n",
    "        n=len(doc_ids), query=query,\n",
    "        candidates=build_candidates_block(doc_ids, corpus),\n",
    "    )\n",
    "    last_err = None\n",
    "    for attempt in range(retries):\n",
    "        try:\n",
    "            resp = client.chat.completions.create(\n",
    "                model=model,\n",
    "                messages=[{\"role\": \"user\", \"content\": prompt}],\n",
    "                temperature=0.0,\n",
    "                max_tokens=300,\n",
    "            )\n",
    "            return parse_ranked_ids(resp.choices[0].message.content, doc_ids)\n",
    "        except Exception as e:\n",
    "            last_err = e\n",
    "            time.sleep(2 ** attempt)\n",
    "    print(f\"[warn] rerank failed: {last_err}; fallback to original order\")\n",
    "    return list(doc_ids)\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "def rerank_all(preds: Dict[str, List[str]], queries: Dict[str, str], corpus: Dict[str, dict],\n",
    "               api_key: str, max_workers: int = MAX_WORKERS) -> Dict[str, List[str]]:\n",
    "    client = OpenAI(api_key=api_key, base_url=\"https://api.deepseek.com\")\n",
    "    out: Dict[str, List[str]] = {}\n",
    "\n",
    "    def worker(qid_dids):\n",
    "        qid, dids = qid_dids\n",
    "        q = queries.get(qid)\n",
    "        if not q:\n",
    "            return qid, list(dids)\n",
    "        return qid, rerank_one(client, q, dids, corpus)\n",
    "\n",
    "    with ThreadPoolExecutor(max_workers=max_workers) as ex:\n",
    "        futures = [ex.submit(worker, item) for item in preds.items()]\n",
    "        for f in tqdm(as_completed(futures), total=len(futures), desc=\"reranking\"):\n",
    "            qid, ranked = f.result()\n",
    "            out[qid] = ranked\n",
    "    return out\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "0f859b63",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "reranked = rerank_all(preds, queries, corpus, api_key=DEEPSEEK_API_KEY)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Сохраним результат, чтобы не гонять API повторно\n",
    "with open(OUT_DIR / \"predictions_reranked.json\", \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n",
    "    json.dump(reranked, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n",
    "print(f\"saved → {OUT_DIR / 'predictions_reranked.json'}\")\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "bfc9df75",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. Метрики после реранжирования"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "dc196a6b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "reranked_metrics = evaluate(reranked, qrels, ks=KS)\n",
    "pd.DataFrame([reranked_metrics]).T.rename(columns={0: \"value\"}).round(4)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "2b2d1b5a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. Сравнительная таблица"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "517dc3cb",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "rows = []\n",
    "for m in baseline:\n",
    "    b, r = baseline[m], reranked_metrics[m]\n",
    "    delta = r - b\n",
    "    delta_pct = (delta / b * 100) if b else 0.0\n",
    "    rows.append({\"metric\": m, \"baseline\": b, \"deepseek_rerank\": r, \"Δ\": delta, \"Δ %\": delta_pct})\n",
    "\n",
    "cmp_df = pd.DataFrame(rows).set_index(\"metric\").round(4)\n",
    "cmp_df\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "4c0cdfb2",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Сохранение результатов\n",
    "cmp_df.to_csv(OUT_DIR / \"comparison.csv\", encoding=\"utf-8\")\n",
    "with open(OUT_DIR / \"comparison.md\", \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n",
    "    f.write(cmp_df.to_markdown())\n",
    "with open(OUT_DIR / \"metrics.json\", \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n",
    "    json.dump({\"baseline\": baseline, \"reranked\": reranked_metrics}, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n",
    "print(\"saved:\", *(p.name for p in OUT_DIR.iterdir()))\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "dc7e03c6",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Замечания\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Модель**: `deepseek-chat` (V3) оптимальна для listwise-реранкинга по соотношению цена/скорость/качество. `deepseek-reasoner` тут избыточен.\n",
    "- **Ключи queries в predictions.json** должны совпадать со столбцом `_id` из split `queries` датасета (в rus-scifact это строки-числа).\n",
    "- **Если в ваших предиктах меньше 10 документов на query**, скрипт всё равно отработает — просто метрики @10 будут считаться по тому, что есть.\n",
    "- **Стоимость**: ~300 queries × ~1.5K промпт-токенов + ~100 ответных ≈ 0.5M токенов на прогон, что у `deepseek-chat` стоит копейки.\n"
   ]
  }
 ],
